modules.description: Provides geolocation data retrieval, including current position and continuous tracking. Works with coordinate structures, timestamps, and error objects. Used to fetch user location in mobile applications and monitor movement in real-time.

Provides functions to extract geographic coordinates, altitude, accuracy, and other position-related data from a position object. Works with custom types representing coordinates, position, error details, and configuration options for location retrieval. Used to fetch the current device location, monitor position changes in real-time, and handle location-related errors with specific error codes and messages.
